p=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2531444\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Aug 04, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104qvl1665702996049.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/qvl1665702996049.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/qvl1665702996049.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"qvl1665702996049\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Configuring for Web Deployment on iSeries\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body taskbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">To set up a Uniface Web environment, you need to configure the various pieces of the Web Application Server architecture to work with each other.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section context\" id=\"qvl1665702996049__context_w1832ab1b5b1_w1833ab1b5_w1834ab1\">\n<div class=\"div context\" id=\"qvl1665702996049__topic_d66701e1_d66702e1_d66703e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"qvl1665702996049__p_d66704e1_d66705e1_d66706e1\">This is best accomplished by a configuration strategy in which you start with a basic configuration, add in the individual components, and test after each step to ensure that the components are working correctly with each other.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"qvl1665702996049__p_d66707e1_d66708e1_d66709e1\">It is assumed that you are familiar with the Uniface architecture and its components, the Web Request Dispatcher (WRD), and Web Services.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"qvl1665702996049__p_d66710e1_d66711e1_d66712e1\">The files you need have been installed in the IFS directory you specified during installation, under <span class=\"ph filepath\">uniface/webapps/uniface</span>. The following steps need to be accomplished in order to configure the WRD on the iSeries in your web server:</p>\n<div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"qvl1665702996049__note_w1835ab1b5b1b1b7_w1836ab1b5b1b1_w1837ab1b5b1_w1838ab1b5_w1839ab1\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span> The following procedures apply to IBM Integrated Web application server for i. For WebSphere, the procedures are very similar.</div>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section><ol class=\"ol steps\"><li class=\"li step\" id=\"qvl1665702996049__li_d29312e1_d29313e1_d29314e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"qnb1665702995328.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/qnb1665702995328.html\" title=\"The IBM Integrated Web application server for i can deploy applications that are in the form of a web archive file, .war file or a web application bundle .wab file. The Uniface Web Request Dispatcher (WRD) servlet is not in this format, so it must be packaged into a .war file.\">Configure the WRD and Create a wrd.war File on iSeries</a>\n</span>\n</li><li class=\"li step\" id=\"qvl1665702996049__li_d29315e1_d29316e1_d29317e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"chy1665702996121.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/chy1665702996121.html\" title=\"You create new application servers on a valid local host.\">Create a New Application Server</a>\n</span>\n</li><li class=\"li step\" id=\"qvl1665702996049__li_d29318e1_d29319e1_d29320e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"mlx1665702995827.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/mlx1665702995827.html\" title=\"You can now deploy the WAR file (wrd.war) you created earlier. See Configure the WRD and Create a wrd.war File on iSeries.\">Install the WRD in the Application Server</a>\n</span>\n</li><li class=\"li step\" id=\"qvl1665702996049__li_d29321e1_d29322e1_d29323e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"zsp1665702996195.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/zsp1665702996195.html\" title=\"You start and test the WRD from an administration page.\">Start and Test the WRD</a>\n</span>\n</li></ol></section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/lmy1665702545752.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Web Services</a><p>A web service is software that makes its functionality available over the Internet.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531444\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531444\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Configuring for Web Deployment on iSeries Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Aug 04, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Configuring for Web Deployment on iSeries To set up a Uniface Web environment, you need to configure the various pieces of the Web Application Server architecture to work with each other. This is best accomplished by a configuration strategy in which you start with a basic configuration, add in the individual components, and test after each step to ensure that the components are working correctly with each other. It is assumed that you are familiar with the Uniface architecture and its components, the Web Request Dispatcher (WRD), and Web Services. The files you need have been installed in the IFS directory you specified during installation, under uniface/webapps/uniface . The following steps need to be accomplished in order to configure the WRD on the iSeries in your web server: Note: The following procedures apply to IBM Integrated Web application server for i. For WebSphere, the procedures are very similar. Configure the WRD and Create a wrd.war File on iSeries Create a New Application Server Install the WRD in the Application Server Start and Test the WRD Related Links Web Services A web service is software that makes its functionality available over the Internet. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}